---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout
  title="Botyoo for E-Commerce — Turn Comments Into Customers"
  description="Automate Instagram DMs for your e-commerce store. Convert post comments into sales conversations, run targeted campaigns, and manage your inbox — all on autopilot."
>
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 pt-36 pb-24">

    {/* Hero */}
    <section class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-24">
      <span class="text-primary font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">For E-Commerce</span>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-balance">
        Turn every Instagram comment into a paying customer
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-muted-foreground text-balance max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        You post a product. Comments flood in. Instead of replying one by one, Botyoo sends a personalized DM to each commenter — with your link, your offer, and your follow-up. Automatically.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a
          href="https://app.botyoo.com/auth/sign-up"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 font-medium shadow-md border-[0.5px] border-white/25 shadow-black/20 bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 h-10 rounded-lg px-6 text-sm transition-colors"
        >
          Start Free
        </a>
        <a
          href="/pricing"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 font-medium ring-1 ring-foreground/10 hover:bg-muted/50 h-10 rounded-lg px-6 text-sm text-foreground transition-colors"
        >
          See Pricing
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* The Journey — Step by Step */}
    <section class="mb-32">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground sm:text-3xl">How it works for your store</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-muted-foreground max-w-xl mx-auto">From a single post to hundreds of sales conversations — here's the full flow.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-20">

        {/* Step 1 */}
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <span class="flex items-center justify-center size-8 rounded-full bg-foreground/10 text-foreground text-sm font-bold">1</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide">You Post</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Drop a product post with a CTA</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
              Post your product — a new drop, a sale, a restock. Add a caption like "Comment LINK to get 20% off" or "Drop 🔥 for the secret discount." That's all you do.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-card/80 ring-1 ring-foreground/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="size-10 rounded-full bg-foreground/10 flex items-center justify-center text-foreground/70 text-sm font-bold">YS</div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">your_store</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Just now</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-foreground/5 rounded-lg aspect-square max-h-40 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">[ Product Image ]</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-foreground/80">
                New summer collection just dropped 🌊<br/>
                Comment <strong>"LINK"</strong> and we'll DM you the exclusive 20% off code.
              </p>
              <div class="border-t border-foreground/10 pt-3 space-y-2">
                <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground"><strong class="text-foreground/70">@emma_style</strong> LINK 🙌</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground"><strong class="text-foreground/70">@mike.fits</strong> link please!</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground"><strong class="text-foreground/70">@sarah_k</strong> LINK 🔥</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Step 2 */}
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="md:order-2">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <span class="flex items-center justify-center size-8 rounded-full bg-foreground/10 text-foreground text-sm font-bold">2</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide">Botyoo Responds</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Every commenter gets a DM — instantly</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
              Within seconds, Botyoo sends a personalized DM to each person who commented the keyword. They get your link, your discount code, and a warm message — no manual work from you.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-card/80 ring-1 ring-foreground/10 rounded-2xl p-6 md:order-1">
            <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
              <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-4">DM to @emma_style</p>
              <div class="flex gap-2">
                <div class="size-6 rounded-full bg-foreground/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <span class="text-foreground/70 text-xs">YS</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-foreground/5 rounded-lg rounded-tl-none p-3 text-muted-foreground">
                  Hey Emma! 👋 Thanks for your interest in the summer collection.
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-2">
                <div class="size-6 rounded-full bg-foreground/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <span class="text-foreground/70 text-xs">YS</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-foreground/5 rounded-lg rounded-tl-none p-3 text-muted-foreground">
                  Here's your exclusive 20% off code: <strong class="text-foreground">SUMMER20</strong><br/><br/>
                  Shop here → yourstore.com/summer
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-2 justify-end">
                <div class="bg-foreground/10 rounded-lg rounded-tr-none p-3 text-foreground">
                  Omg thank you! Ordering now 🛒
                </div>
                <div class="size-6 rounded-full bg-foreground/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <span class="text-foreground/70 text-xs">E</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Step 3 */}
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <span class="flex items-center justify-center size-8 rounded-full bg-foreground/10 text-foreground text-sm font-bold">3</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide">Follow-Up</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Didn't buy? Follow up automatically</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
              Set up a follow-up sequence. If they didn't click the link within 24 hours, Botyoo sends a gentle reminder. After 3 days, maybe a "last chance" message. All automated.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-card/80 ring-1 ring-foreground/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <div class="space-y-4 text-sm">
              <p class="font-medium text-foreground">Follow-up sequence</p>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-foreground/5">
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground w-16 shrink-0">After 1d</span>
                  <p class="text-muted-foreground text-xs">"Hey! Just checking — did you get a chance to check out the summer collection? Your code SUMMER20 is still active 🌊"</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-foreground/5">
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground w-16 shrink-0">After 3d</span>
                  <p class="text-muted-foreground text-xs">"Last chance! Your 20% off expires tonight. Don't miss out → yourstore.com/summer"</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-foreground/5">
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground w-16 shrink-0">After 7d</span>
                  <p class="text-muted-foreground text-xs">"New arrivals just dropped! Want early access? Reply YES and I'll send you the link before anyone else 👀"</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Step 4 */}
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="md:order-2">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <span class="flex items-center justify-center size-8 rounded-full bg-foreground/10 text-foreground text-sm font-bold">4</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide">Campaigns</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Run DM campaigns to your contact list</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
              Got a flash sale? New product? Restock alert? Send a bulk DM campaign to all your captured contacts — filtered by tag, automation, or both. Way better open rates than email.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-card/80 ring-1 ring-foreground/10 rounded-2xl p-6 md:order-1">
            <div class="space-y-4 text-sm">
              <p class="font-medium text-foreground">Campaign: Flash Sale Alert</p>
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div class="flex justify-between text-xs">
                  <span class="text-muted-foreground">Audience</span>
                  <span class="text-foreground/70">Summer Collection leads</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-xs">
                  <span class="text-muted-foreground">Contacts</span>
                  <span class="text-foreground/70">1,247</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-xs">
                  <span class="text-muted-foreground">Status</span>
                  <span class="text-foreground/70">Sending...</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="border-t border-foreground/10 pt-3">
                <div class="bg-foreground/5 rounded-lg p-3 text-muted-foreground text-xs">
                  "Hey {`{name}`}! 🚨 Flash sale — 40% off everything for the next 6 hours. Use code FLASH40 → yourstore.com/sale"
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between text-xs pt-2">
                <span class="text-muted-foreground">Sent: 892</span>
                <span class="text-muted-foreground">Delivered: 98.2%</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Step 5 */}
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <span class="flex items-center justify-center size-8 rounded-full bg-foreground/10 text-foreground text-sm font-bold">5</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide">Inbox</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Manage all conversations in one inbox</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
              When customers reply with questions — sizing, shipping, returns — your team handles it from one shared inbox. No switching between Instagram and other tools. Reply, tag, assign, done.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-card/80 ring-1 ring-foreground/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
              <p class="font-medium text-foreground">Inbox</p>
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-foreground/5">
                  <div class="size-8 rounded-full bg-foreground/10 flex items-center justify-center text-foreground/70 text-xs font-bold">EK</div>
                  <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                    <p class="text-foreground font-medium text-xs">@emma_style</p>
                    <p class="text-muted-foreground text-xs truncate">"What size should I get? I'm usually a M"</p>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">2m</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-foreground/5">
                  <div class="size-8 rounded-full bg-foreground/10 flex items-center justify-center text-foreground/70 text-xs font-bold">MF</div>
                  <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                    <p class="text-foreground font-medium text-xs">@mike.fits</p>
                    <p class="text-muted-foreground text-xs truncate">"Do you ship to Canada?"</p>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">5m</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-foreground/5">
                  <div class="size-8 rounded-full bg-foreground/10 flex items-center justify-center text-foreground/70 text-xs font-bold">SK</div>
                  <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                    <p class="text-foreground font-medium text-xs">@sarah_k</p>
                    <p class="text-muted-foreground text-xs truncate">"Order placed! When does it ship?"</p>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">12m</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Results */}
    <section class="mb-32">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground sm:text-3xl">What e-commerce brands see</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-card/80 ring-1 ring-foreground/10 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-foreground">3–5×</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-2">Higher conversion than email</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card/80 ring-1 ring-foreground/10 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-foreground">90%+</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-2">DM open rate</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card/80 ring-1 ring-foreground/10 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-foreground">0 min</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-2">Manual reply time</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Use Cases */}
    <section class="mb-32">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground sm:text-3xl">Perfect for</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-card/80 ring-1 ring-foreground/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Product Launches</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Tease a new product, collect "interested" comments, DM everyone the link on launch day.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card/80 ring-1 ring-foreground/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Flash Sales</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Run a 6-hour sale and blast your entire contact list with a DM campaign. 90%+ open rate.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card/80 ring-1 ring-foreground/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Restock Alerts</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Sold out? Collect "notify me" comments. When it's back, DM everyone automatically.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card/80 ring-1 ring-foreground/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Discount Codes</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Gate exclusive codes behind a follow. Grow your audience and drive sales at the same time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* CTA */}
    <section class="text-center py-16 border-t border-foreground/10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground sm:text-3xl mb-4">
        Ready to turn comments into revenue?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto">
        Set up your first automation in under 5 minutes. No credit card required.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://app.botyoo.com/auth/sign-up"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 font-medium shadow-md border-[0.5px] border-white/25 shadow-black/20 bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 h-11 rounded-lg px-8 text-sm transition-colors"
      >
        Start Free — No Card Required
      </a>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
